It includes detailed rate information for different usage periods (peak, off-peak, shoulder) and types (commodity, demand, delivery). The table also tracks metadata such as the user who authenticated the entry and timestamps for when the data was added or last updated. This table is crucial for financial forecasting and budgeting within an organization, particularly in sectors dealing with utilities or energy where usage rates fluctuate based on time and demand.
